OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Women's freedoms have been further     
OL,6, curtailed in Afghanistan, after the    
OL,7, Taliban barred them from working for   
OL,8, non-governmental organisations (NGOs). 
OL,10,FThe Islamist rulers said female NGO    
OL,11,Fstaff had broken strict dress codes.   
OL,13,FThe edict has been condemned by the    
OL,14,Forganisations themselves, as well as   
OL,15,Fthe UN. It comes just days after female
OL,16,Fstudents were banned from universities.
OL,18,FFemale Afghan NGO workers acting as the
OL,19,Fmain earners in their household told   
OL,20,Fthe BBC of their fear and helplessness.
